    "body": "I am also seeing this error when trying to deploy to mumbai or polygon mainnet with `forge script`:\r\n\r\n`(code: -32000, message: tx fee (31817737348228659071582317996769352666291978645262041088.00 ether) exceeds the configured cap (1.00 ether), data: None)`\r\n\r\nThis exact error is also intermittent. The deploy always fails, but sometimes it fails with this error message instead:\r\n`(code: -32000, message: insufficient funds for gas * price + value, data: None)`\r\n\r\nThe Estimated amount required is very small, and the wallet that is deploying definitely has sufficient funds:\r\n```\r\n==========================\r\nChain 137\r\nEstimated total gas used for script: 133391\r\nEstimated amount required: 0.00491102552563229 ETH\r\n==========================\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd I'm able to deploy to other networks no problem.",
